Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:04.81,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,あぁ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,勝ったわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:07.89,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:08.35,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,勝った！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.72,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,いいぞ！鮎原さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.20,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,やっと勝ったよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.78,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,本当にやったのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.93,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,お目出度う！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:25.12,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,皆！
